Command Line: <strong><%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.cmdline %></strong>
<br>
Command Name: <strong><%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.command_name %></strong>
<br>
CPU Usage: <strong><%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.cpu_usage.round(2) %>%</strong>
<br>
Last Executed CPU: <strong><%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.last_executed_cpu %></strong>
<br>
Threads: <strong><%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.threads %></strong>
<br>
Memory: <%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.memory.then { |x|
	unless x
		'Info Not Available'.freeze
	else
		"<strong>#{x.fdiv(1000)} MiB</strong>".html_safe
	end
}%>
<br>
IO: <%= LinuxStat::ProcessInfo.total_io.then { |x|
	if x.empty?
		'Info Not Available'.freeze
	else
		"Read: <strong>#{x[:read_bytes].fdiv(1000 ** 2).round(2)} MiB</strong> | "\
		"Write: <strong>#{x[:write_bytes].fdiv(1000 ** 2).round(2)} MiB</strong>".html_safe
	end
} %>
